headline: What You Need To Know Ahead of Robinhood Markets' Earnings Release
summary: Robinhood Markets is gearing up to release its fourth-quarter results next month, and analysts are expecting a single-digit rise in earnings.

headline: Listen Labs raises $69 million Series B to bring customer voices into every decision
summary: Listen Labs, the AI-first customer research platform, has raised a $69 million Series B led by Ribbit Capital, with participation from Evantic and existing investors Sequoia Capital, Conviction, and Pear VC.
